    {
      "text": "A 52-year-old woman with diabetes presents with 4 days of left flank pain and fever. She was prescribed oral ciprofloxacin three days ago at urgent care for presumed pyelonephritis but reports worsening symptoms. Vital signs are BP, 125/75; P, 105; T, 38.7°C (101.7°F). Physical examination shows left costovertebral angle tenderness. Laboratory studies show leukocytosis, and urinalysis shows pyuria and bacteriuria. What is the most appropriate next step in management?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Intravenous pyelogram"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Admission for IV antibiotics"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "CT abdomen and pelvis with contrast"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Discharge with levofloxacin"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "text": "Blood cultures and observation"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 3,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=c50aQg&anker=Z19727703c74c14a6b2a5369d56a7263e\" data-learningcard-id=\"c50aQg\" data-anker=\"Z19727703c74c14a6b2a5369d56a7263e\" data-section-id=\"8McOq10\" data-sememe-id=\"AdYRsL\">Intravenous pyelogram</a> is an outdated imaging modality that was previously used to evaluate for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ni0-7f&anker=Zc73fc3dea6689aacbf97773ad1038288\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ni0-7f\" data-anker=\"Zc73fc3dea6689aacbf97773ad1038288\" data-sememe-id=\"vl0AAT\">urinary tract obstruction</a> and congenital abnormalities. However, CT with contrast is now the preferred imaging study for suspected <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hi0KGf&anker=Za1d6bf136f886395095a2dfbad95f169\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hi0KGf\" data-anker=\"Za1d6bf136f886395095a2dfbad95f169\" data-section-id=\"oR10Lg0\" data-sememe-id=\"LCcwse0\">complicated pyelonephritis</a>, as it provides superior visualization of renal <span data-sememe-id=\"srXtiz\">parenchyma</span> and perinephric structures compared to IVP.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) INCORRECT:</h4>While broad-spectrum intravenous <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\">antibiotics</a> are appropriate for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hi0KGf&anker=Za1d6bf136f886395095a2dfbad95f169\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hi0KGf\" data-anker=\"Za1d6bf136f886395095a2dfbad95f169\" data-section-id=\"oR10Lg0\" data-sememe-id=\"LCcwse0\">complicated pyelonephritis</a>, initiating <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\">antibiotic therapy</a> alone without imaging would be inadequate in this diabetic patient with persistent symptoms despite prior treatment. <span data-sememe-id=\"-jWD1l0\">Cross-sectional imaging</span> is essential to evaluate for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=si0tGf&anker=Zd365224c2be8064248f7daaeb6831d7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"si0tGf\" data-anker=\"Zd365224c2be8064248f7daaeb6831d7c\" data-sememe-id=\"0N0e-T\">perinephric abscess</a>, as <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3g0SE2&anker=Z1235e572dd827cff7d31e954b3f94489\" data-learningcard-id=\"3g0SE2\" data-anker=\"Z1235e572dd827cff7d31e954b3f94489\" data-sememe-id=\"a40Q3T\">diabetes</a> is a major <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ps0LDh&anker=Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-learningcard-id=\"ps0LDh\" data-anker=\"Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-section-id=\"FfWgLk0\" data-sememe-id=\"b31HSg0\">risk factor</a> for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=aq0QCS&anker=Zc5e4bc5f6a9a7188f4806603b26e8234\" data-learningcard-id=\"aq0QCS\" data-anker=\"Zc5e4bc5f6a9a7188f4806603b26e8234\" data-section-id=\"zc1rUf0\" data-sememe-id=\"yVbdCs\">abscess</a> formation.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) CORRECT:</h4>Correct -- CT abdomen and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=A60RnS&anker=Z302395fa53b6096eda0d6a50e247fdd4\" data-learningcard-id=\"A60RnS\" data-anker=\"Z302395fa53b6096eda0d6a50e247fdd4\" data-section-id=\"lEcvDV0\" data-sememe-id=\"ZyXZd00\">pelvis</a> with contrast is indicated for this patient with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3g0SE2&anker=Z1235e572dd827cff7d31e954b3f94489\" data-learningcard-id=\"3g0SE2\" data-anker=\"Z1235e572dd827cff7d31e954b3f94489\" data-sememe-id=\"a40Q3T\">diabetes</a> who has persistent flank <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=xN0EWg&anker=Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-learningcard-id=\"xN0EWg\" data-anker=\"Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-section-id=\"NBX-a00\">pain</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j50_Pg&anker=Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-learningcard-id=\"j50_Pg\" data-anker=\"Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-sememe-id=\"CL0q-g\">fever</a> despite <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\">antibiotic</a> treatment. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3g0SE2&anker=Z1235e572dd827cff7d31e954b3f94489\" data-learningcard-id=\"3g0SE2\" data-anker=\"Z1235e572dd827cff7d31e954b3f94489\" data-sememe-id=\"a40Q3T\">Diabetes</a> is a major <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ps0LDh&anker=Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-learningcard-id=\"ps0LDh\" data-anker=\"Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-section-id=\"FfWgLk0\" data-sememe-id=\"b31HSg0\">risk factor</a> for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=si0tGf&anker=Zd365224c2be8064248f7daaeb6831d7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"si0tGf\" data-anker=\"Zd365224c2be8064248f7daaeb6831d7c\" data-sememe-id=\"0N0e-T\">perinephric abscess</a>, and failure to improve with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\">antibiotics</a> in this high-risk population warrants <span data-sememe-id=\"-jWD1l0\">cross-sectional imaging</span> to evaluate for complications.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>Switching to oral <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z6b160289536b8a7a7a2c161a02014e7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z6b160289536b8a7a7a2c161a02014e7c\" data-section-id=\"VjcGzX0\" data-sememe-id=\"lL0vBg\">fluoroquinolone</a> therapy would be inappropriate given the patient's clinical deterioration and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ps0LDh&anker=Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-learningcard-id=\"ps0LDh\" data-anker=\"Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-section-id=\"FfWgLk0\" data-sememe-id=\"b31HSg0\">risk factors</a>. The failure to respond to initial <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\">antibiotic therapy</a> suggests a complication requiring further evaluation.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7l04yT&anker=Zbbc1ac48182c8850d109967ff3d2e390\" data-learningcard-id=\"7l04yT\" data-anker=\"Zbbc1ac48182c8850d109967ff3d2e390\" data-sememe-id=\"kn0mtg\">Blood cultures</a> are important but delaying imaging in a patient with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3g0SE2&anker=Z1235e572dd827cff7d31e954b3f94489\" data-learningcard-id=\"3g0SE2\" data-anker=\"Z1235e572dd827cff7d31e954b3f94489\" data-sememe-id=\"a40Q3T\">diabetes</a> and worsening <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hi0KGf&anker=Z9b1fc059a71fe47b61063c80c81af8c3\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hi0KGf\" data-anker=\"Z9b1fc059a71fe47b61063c80c81af8c3\" data-sememe-id=\"ZN0Z-T\">pyelonephritis</a> symptoms despite <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\">antibiotic therapy</a> could result in missed diagnosis of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=si0tGf&anker=Zd365224c2be8064248f7daaeb6831d7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"si0tGf\" data-anker=\"Zd365224c2be8064248f7daaeb6831d7c\" data-sememe-id=\"0N0e-T\">perinephric abscess</a> and subsequent complications.</div>",
